written for centos 7.4

ip addresses use the internal ip to connect to nagios

dynamic directory enabled !!! 
don't run the playbook if you don't know what you are doing, 
it will deploy it to the aws cloud if your computer is setup correctly


to run the playbook type
# ansible-playbook nagios.yml --ask-vault-pass 

the ec2 instances should be tagged with tag_monitor_nagios and tag_Name_Nagios
tag_monitor_nagios: all servers
tag_Name_Nagios: nagios server
